text: Mahammed Boun Abdallah Dionne (22 September 1959 - 5 April 2024) was a Senegalese politician. He was the Prime Minister of Senegal from 2014 to 2019. He is the third prime minister appointed by President Macky Sall. He was the last prime minister of the country. Dionne died on April 5, 2024, in Paris, where he had been sent to for medical treatment in the middle of his election campaign. He was 64.Sénégal : décès de M.
